                <div class="alert alert-danger" style="background-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1); border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);">
                    <p class="mb-2"><strong>Your selected date range exceeds the maximum allowed duration.</strong></p>
                    <hr style="border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);">
                    <p class="mb-1">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-calendar-x me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                            <path d="M6.146 7.146a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0L8 8.293l1.146-1.147a.5.5 0 1 1 .708.708L8.707 9l1.147 1.146a.5.5 0 0 1-.708.708L8 9.707l-1.146 1.147a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L7.293 9 6.146 7.854a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708z"/>
                            <path d="M3.5 0a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5V1h8V.5a.5.5 0 0 1 1 0V1h1a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h1V.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5zM1 4v10a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h12a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V4H1z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <strong>Selected duration:</strong> <span id="selectedDays" class="text-danger">0</span> days
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-calendar-check me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                            <path d="M10.854 7.146a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-3 3a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-1.5-1.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708L7.5 9.793l2.646-2.647a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0z"/>
                            <path d="M3.5 0a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5V1h8V.5a.5.5 0 0 1 1 0V1h1a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h1V.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5zM1 4v10a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h12a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V4H1z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <strong>Maximum allowed:</strong> <span class="text-success">@ViewData["MaxMealPlanDays"]</span> days
                    </p>
                </div>
                <p class="text-center mb-0">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="#22c55e" class="bi bi-info-circle me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14zm0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16z"/>
                        <path d="m8.93 6.588-2.29.287-.082.38.45.083c.294.07.352.176.288.469l-.738 3.468c-.194.897.105 1.319.808 1.319.545 0 1.178-.252 1.465-.598l.088-.416c-.2.176-.492.246-.686.246-.275 0-.375-.193-.304-.533L8.93 6.588zM9 4.5a1 1 0 1 1-2 0 1 1 0 0 1 2 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                    The end date has been automatically adjusted to the maximum allowed duration.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-success" data-bs-dismiss="modal">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14zm0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16z"/>
                        <path d="M10.97 4.97a.235.235 0 0 0-.02.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-1.071-1.05z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Got It
